'''Al Muharraq Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] situated in [[Arad, Bahrain|Arad]], [[Bahrain]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Muharraq Club]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Muharraq enter King Cup semis|url=http://www.gulf-daily-news.com/NewsDetails.aspx?storyid=208871|accessdate=16 December 2012|newspaper=Gulf Daily News|date=16 February 2008}}</ref>  The stadium holds 10,000 people. 

The stadium underwent maintenance works for a month during September 2012.<ref>{{cite web|title=Al Haj: Muharraq Club Stadium is 50% ready after three weeks of maintenance.|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-303150014.html|publisher=Bahrain News Agency (via [[HighBeam Research]])|accessdate=16 December 2012}}</ref>

