{| class="infobox football" style="width: 16em; text-align: center;" |- ! style="font-size: 16px;" | Balram Smriti Kaski District League |- | style="font-size: 12px; background: #BFD7FF;" | '''Current Champions (2012-13)''' |- | style="font-size: 12px;" | [[Garden Football Club]] |} '''Balram Smriti Kaski District League''' is a semi-professional local district division of the [[All Nepal Football Association]] in [[Nepal]]. Contested by clubs of [[Kaski District|Kaski]] district [[Nepal]].<ref>http://www.goalnepal.com/news.php?id=11101</ref> The tournament is played in league-cum-knockout format. The league stage is divided in groups and winners move on to the knockout stage. The winner of the tournament represent Kaski in further regional and [[Nepal National League]].
