{{Infobox stadium |stadium_name = Estadio Antonio Herrera Gutiérrez |nickname = |image = |caption = |fullname = |location = [[Barquisimeto]], [[Venezuela]] |built = |opened = 1969 |renovated = |closed = |demolished = |owner = |operator = |construction_cost = |tenants = <center>[[Cardenales de Lara]]</center> |seating_capacity = 20,450| }}
'''Estadio Antonio Herrera Gutiérrez''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Barquisimeto]], [[Venezuela]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://noticiaaldia.com/2013/06/el-rey-david-concepcion-llega-a-65-anos-de-vida-felicitaciones-fotos/ |title=El "Rey" David Concepción llega a 65 años de vida… ¡Felicitaciones! (+fotos) |date=17 June 2013 |work=Noticia Al Dia |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HdnEnnA6?url=http://noticiaaldia.com/2013/06/el-rey-david-concepcion-llega-a-65-anos-de-vida-felicitaciones-fotos/ |archivedate=25 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref> It is currently used mostly for [[baseball]] games and serves as the home of [[Cardenales de Lara]]. The stadium holds 20,450 people.
